@startuml Profile Management Flow
!theme vibrant
title LilyFit - Profile Management Flow

actor User
participant "ProfileScreen" as ProfileUI
participant "EditProfileDialog" as EditDialog
participant "AppProvider" as Provider
participant "UserProfile" as Profile
participant "SupabaseService" as Supabase
participant "ImagePicker" as ImagePick

== View Profile ==

User -> ProfileUI: Navigate to Profile tab
activate ProfileUI

ProfileUI -> Provider: Get user profile
activate Provider
Provider --> ProfileUI: UserProfile data
deactivate Provider

ProfileUI --> User: Display profile:\n- Name, Email\n- Age, Gender\n- Weight, Height (with units)\n- Activity Level\n- Goal\n- Target Macros\n- BMI & Category\n- Current streak

== Edit Profile ==

User -> ProfileUI: Click "Edit Profile" button

ProfileUI -> EditDialog: Show edit dialog
activate EditDialog

EditDialog -> Provider: Get current profile
activate Provider
Provider --> EditDialog: UserProfile
deactivate Provider

EditDialog --> User: Show edit form:\n- Name\n- Gender (Male/Female/Other)\n- Age slider\n- Weight slider (with unit toggle)\n- Height slider (with unit toggle)\n- Activity level dropdown\n- Goal selection

== Update Basic Info ==

User -> EditDialog: Update name
User -> EditDialog: Change gender
User -> EditDialog: Adjust age (e.g., 30)
User -> EditDialog: Preview changes

EditDialog -> Profile: Create updated profile object
Profile -> Profile: Validate changes

EditDialog --> User: Show live preview of:\n- New BMI\n- Updated calorie target\n- New macro targets

== Update Physical Stats ==

User -> EditDialog: Toggle unit (kg → lbs)

EditDialog -> EditDialog: Convert displayed value:\n75 kg → 165.3 lbs

User -> EditDialog: Adjust weight to 170 lbs
User -> EditDialog: Adjust height to 6'0"

EditDialog -> Profile: Convert to metric:\nweight: 77.1 kg\nheight: 183 cm

== Update Activity & Goals ==

User -> EditDialog: Change activity level:\n"Moderate" → "Active"

EditDialog -> Profile: Set activityLevel = "active"
EditDialog -> Profile: Preview new TDEE:\n1.55x → 1.725x multiplier

User -> EditDialog: Change goal:\n"Maintenance" → "Fat Loss"

EditDialog -> Profile: Set goal = "fatLoss"
EditDialog -> Profile: Preview calorie adjustment:\nTDEE - 500 calories

== Calculate New Targets ==

User -> EditDialog: Click "Save Changes"

EditDialog -> Profile: calculateTargets()
activate Profile

Profile -> Profile: **Step 1: Calculate BMR**\n(Mifflin-St Jeor Equation)
note right
  For Male, Age 30, 77.1kg, 183cm:
  BMR = 10*77.1 + 6.25*183 - 5*30 + 5
      = 771 + 1143.75 - 150 + 5
      = 1769.75 kcal
end note

Profile -> Profile: **Step 2: Apply Activity**\nTDEE = BMR * 1.725

note right
  TDEE = 1769.75 * 1.725
       = 3052.8 kcal
end note

Profile -> Profile: **Step 3: Apply Goal**\nTarget = TDEE - 500

note right
  For Fat Loss:
  Target = 3052.8 - 500
         = 2552.8 kcal
end note

Profile -> Profile: **Step 4: Calculate Macros**

note right
  Fat Loss macro split (40% P, 30% C, 30% F):

  Protein = 2552.8 * 0.40 / 4 = 255g
  Carbs = 2552.8 * 0.30 / 4 = 192g
  Fat = 2552.8 * 0.30 / 9 = 85g
end note

Profile --> EditDialog: Targets calculated
deactivate Profile

EditDialog --> User: Show final confirmation:\n- New calories: 2553 kcal\n- Protein: 255g\n- Carbs: 192g\n- Fat: 85g

User -> EditDialog: Confirm "Save"

== Save Profile ==

EditDialog -> Provider: updateProfile(profile)
activate Provider

Provider -> Profile: Validate all fields
Provider -> Provider: Save to SharedPreferences
Provider -> Provider: notifyListeners()
Provider --> EditDialog: Profile updated locally
deactivate Provider

EditDialog -> Supabase: saveUserProfile(profile)
activate Supabase

alt Save Successful
    Supabase --> EditDialog: Profile synced to cloud
    deactivate Supabase

    EditDialog --> User: Show success message:\n"✅ Profile updated!"

    EditDialog -> ProfileUI: Close dialog
    deactivate EditDialog

    ProfileUI -> Provider: Refresh profile data
    activate Provider
    Provider --> ProfileUI: Updated profile
    deactivate Provider

    ProfileUI --> User: Display updated profile:\n- New targets visible\n- Adjusted daily goals\n- Recalculated BMI

else Save Failed
    Supabase --> EditDialog: Error
    deactivate Supabase

    EditDialog --> User: Show error:\n"Failed to sync profile.\nChanges saved locally."

    note right of EditDialog
      Local changes are preserved
      even if cloud sync fails.
      Will retry on next app launch.
    end note
end

== Change Profile Photo ==

User -> ProfileUI: Click on profile avatar
activate ProfileUI

ProfileUI -> ImagePick: Pick image
activate ImagePick

ImagePick --> User: Show image picker:\n- Camera\n- Gallery

User -> ImagePick: Select photo from gallery

ImagePick -> ImagePick: Compress & resize image
ImagePick --> ProfileUI: Return image file
deactivate ImagePick

ProfileUI -> Supabase: Upload profile image
activate Supabase

Supabase -> Supabase: Store in storage bucket
Supabase --> ProfileUI: Image URL
deactivate Supabase

ProfileUI -> Provider: Update profile photo URL
activate Provider
Provider -> Provider: Save URL to profile
Provider -> Provider: Cache image locally
Provider --> ProfileUI: Photo updated
deactivate Provider

ProfileUI --> User: Display new profile photo
deactivate ProfileUI

== View Macro Calculator ==

User -> ProfileUI: Click "Macro Calculator" info icon
activate ProfileUI

ProfileUI --> User: Show explanation modal:\n\n**How we calculate your targets:**\n\n1. BMR (Basal Metabolic Rate)\n   Mifflin-St Jeor Equation\n\n2. TDEE (Total Daily Energy)\n   BMR × Activity Multiplier\n\n3. Goal Adjustment\n   - Fat Loss: TDEE - 500\n   - Maintenance: TDEE\n   - Muscle Gain: TDEE + 300\n\n4. Macro Distribution\n   Based on your goal

User -> ProfileUI: Close modal
deactivate ProfileUI

@enduml

